The Orient pendant is a flawless light design with good luminous efficacy and made from the finest quality materials.

item.content:encoded: The Knit-Wit lamp is a true craftsmanship with timeless, refined design. Its made with 3D knitting technique, without any cut-offs and sewing, in fact – there is no waste of yarn at all. Inspired by the lightning sphere of the sun and the traditional Chinese rice lamp.
